org.dspace.search

Class QueryResults

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dspace.search.QueryResults
  • Deprecated. 
    Since DSpace 4 the system use an abstraction layer named Discovery to provide access to different search provider. The legacy system build upon Apache Lucene is likely to be removed in a future version. If you are interested in use Lucene as backend for the DSpace search system please consider to build a Lucene implementation of the Discovery interfaces

    @Deprecated
public class QueryResults
extends Object
    Contains the results of a query. Use access methods to examine and retrieve the results.
